Subject: Re: [T2] Restomotive "Metal Ready"

You can buy phosphoric acid from any auto paint shop.  Does the same thing.  
Put it on.  Let it sit for awhile, the deeper the rust the longer it has to 
be kept wet with phosphoric acid.  Rinse with water,  Let it dry and it is 
ready for sanding or paint.
Timk11
